{{Infobox language |name=Osatu |nativename= |states=[[Cameroon]] |speakers=400 |date=2002 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Benue–Congo]] |fam4=[[Southern Bantoid]] |fam5=[[Grassfields languages|Grassfields]] |fam6=[[Southwest Grassfields languages|Southwest]] |iso3=ost |glotto=osat1238 |glottorefname=Osatu }}
'''Osatu''' (Ihatum) is a [[Grassfields language]] of [[Cameroon]].
Osatu is poorly documented and for a time had been considered a [[Tivoid language]].
